content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Search by action available for URL click tracking logs in Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection July 19, 2024 – Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection adds a new search criterion (Action: Restricted) in URL click tracking logs. Using this criterion, administrators are able to filter out URLs with actions "Blocked", "Warned and accessed", and "Warned and stopped”.
